		</div>
		<div class="col-md-5" style="padding: 35px;">
			<h3><%=link_to "Inventory", "inventory", class: "individualportfolio"%> </h3>
    	<p>A hackweek project - 1 week to create a useful app from scratch. This app allows you to log the items in your cupboards, automatically put them on the shoppping list when you are running low and suggest recipes you can make with the items you currently have</p>
			<p><strong>Best feature: </strong>A couple of API calls allowing me to scan items in on my phone and look them up bfore adding them to the inventory </p>
		</div>
